The paper deals with computational mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves the analysis of algorithms and complexity theory, which are related to data structures (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically focuses on combinatorial auctions, which are a topic in algorithmic game theory (cs.EC) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
